{
  "stem": "27687.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But oh boy, these poor man and boys, it was terrible, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was bleeding.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had to go and had the bandage done and everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Yeah, and he was laughing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was, and if somebody wasn't laying down and crawling like a snake, he had the whip and whipped on the, in the back, you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So anyhow",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The death march.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the 22nd of January, 1945.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got assembled and each one got a, a blanket plus our clothes and shoes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we marched.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Most of these people what were not electrician, but were just laborers and working in other, they had this striped uniform and they have wooden shoes with the cloth upper, with you know, laces.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had leather shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The first day of the march, was late in the evening when we came to a farmhouse.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the farmhouse owner, with the farmer, he gave us potatoes, potatoes what he feeds the pigs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we were happy to have that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then he opened up the farm, a barn.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He opened up a barn and we went in the barn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The barn was with straw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And while we were laying there to have rest, we noticed that there is lots of grain still on the, on the-",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the wheat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we were all eating this grain, taking out grain, and eating the grain and was not too bad.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so the next day, we were feeling not too bad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everybody had enough to eat, I guess.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we started to march again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The next night.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "SS.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The next evening we came to a farm house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And again, the same thing, but he gave us a different kind of vegetables and potatoes.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
